<surface xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:mith="http://mith.umd.edu/sc/ns1#" ulx="0"
  uly="0" lrx="5372" lry="7222" xml:id="ox-ms_shelley_e2-0078" partOf="#ox-ms_shelley_e2" mith:folio="38v" mith:shelfmark="MS. Shelley e. 2">
  <graphic url="http://shelleygodwinarchive.org/images/ox/ox-ms_shelley_e2-0078.jp2"/>
  <zone type="main">
    <line>From<mod>
        <del rend="strikethrough">pyramids</del>
        <add place="superlinear">icy spires</add>
      </mod> of sunlike radiance fling</line>
    <line>The dawn, as lifted Oceans dazzling spray</line>
    <line>From some Atlantic islet scattered up</line>
    <line>Spangles the wind with lamp-like water drops</line>
    <line>The vale is girdled with their walls&#8212;a howl</line>
    <line>Of cataracts from their thaw clove'n ravines</line>
    <line>Satiates the listening wind, continuous, vast,</line>
    <line>Awful as silence&#8212;hark! the rushing snow</line>
    <line>The sun-awakened avalanche, whose mass</line>
    <line>Thrice sifted by the storm <mod>
        <del rend="overwritten">s</del>
        <add place="intralinear">h</add>
      </mod>ad gathered there</line>
    <line>Flake after flake: in Heaven-defying minds</line>
    <milestone unit="tei:l" spanTo="#e2-0078.01"/>
    <line>As thought by thought is piled, till some great</line>
    <line rend="right">truth</line>
    <anchor xml:id="e2-0078.01"/>
    <line>Is loosened, &amp; the <mod>
        <del rend="strikethrough">mountains</del>
        <add place="superlinear">nations</add>
      </mod> echo round</line>
    <line>Shaken to their roots: as do the mountains now.</line>
    <milestone unit="tei:speaker" spanTo="#e2-0078.02"/>
    <line rend="center">Panthea</line>
    <anchor xml:id="e2-0078.02"/>
    <line rend="indent1">Look <unclear reason="illegible">;</unclear> how the gusty sea of mist is
      breaking</line>
    <line rend="indent1">In crimson foam even at our feet&#8212;it rises</line>
    <line rend="indent1">As Ocean at the inchantment of the moon</line>
    <line rend="left"><add><metamark function="count">310</metamark></add></line>
  </zone>
</surface>
